{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775818094632,"sessionID":"ses_288ffc1e7ffeibQkrb4gwKYkT4","part":{"id":"prt_d77005ab90017iaNmYKHCw4TI4","messageID":"msg_d77004aa7001YI1RzH0OxPymd2","sessionID":"ses_288ffc1e7ffeibQkrb4gwKYkT4","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_093fe5a974fc4f7ca216c106","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project structure, focusing on:\n1. Find the pkg/workloadmanager directory and list all files in it\n2. Look for any existing spec files (delta-spec.md, spec.md, etc.)\n3. Search for any files related to \"sandbox\", \"lifecycle\", \"delete\" in the project\n4. Check if there's an openspec directory or similar\n\nReturn:\n- Full listing of pkg/workloadmanager directory\n- Any existing spec files found\n- Key files related to sandbox/lifecycle/delete\n- The project root structure","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_288ff99b7ffeZizvkJWwC820I1 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is the complete exploration report of the agentcube project.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Full Listing of `pkg/workloadmanager` Directory\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  handler/\n    constants.go        (53 lines)   -- GVRs, kind constants, label/annotation keys, default TTL/idle values\n    models.go           (57 lines)   -- CreateSandboxRequest/Response, SandboxInfo, SandboxStatus structs\n    sandbox_create.go   (687 lines)  -- SandboxCreateHandler with CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox, CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox, buildCR, resolvePodIP, rollbackCR, etc.\n  middleware/\n    (empty directory -- no files)\n  response/\n    response.go         (45 lines)   -- JSON, Created, Error, ErrorWithID helper functions\n    response_test.go    (test file)\n```\n\n**Key observation:** The `middleware/` directory exists but is empty. There is no `sandbox_delete.go` or any delete handler file yet -- only creation logic exists in `sandbox_create.go`. The `sandbox_create.go` file does contain a `rollbackCR` method (line 363-372) that deletes a CR on failure, but there is no dedicated delete-by-session endpoint handler implemented.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Existing Spec Files Found\n\n### Root-level spec files:\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| delta-spec.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` |\n| test_spec.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` |\n\n### Feature directory spec files:\n| Feature | Path |\n|---------|------|\n| sandbox-orchestration | `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` (176 lines) |\n| idle-cleanup | `idle-cleanup/spec.md` (69 lines) |\n| ci-cd | `ci-cd/spec.md` |\n| cli-toolkit | `cli-toolkit/spec.md` |\n| code-execution | `code-execution/spec.md` |\n| deployment | `deployment/spec.md` |\n| integrations | `integrations/spec.md` |\n| python-sdk | `python-sdk/spec.md` |\n| session-store | `session-store/spec.md` |\n| session-routing | `session-routing/spec.md` |\n\n### Changes directory delta-spec files:\n| Change | Path |\n|--------|------|\n| AR-002 | `changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md` |\n| AR-003 | `changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md` |\n| AR-004 | `changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md` (227 lines -- WorkloadManager HTTP service framework) |\n| AR-005 | `changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md` |\n\n**No `openspec` directory** was found anywhere in the project.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Key Files Related to Sandbox / Lifecycle / Delete\n\n### Primary sandbox lifecycle files:\n\n| File | Path | Relevance |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| sandbox_create.go | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go` | Sandbox creation, CR building, pod IP resolution, rollback on failure |\n| constants.go | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go` | GVRs (SandboxGVR, SandboxClaimGVR), kind constants, labels/annotations |\n| models.go | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models.go` | SandboxInfo, CreateSandboxRequest/Response structs |\n| sandbox-orchestration/spec.md | `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` | Full spec including **Delete sandbox by session** (line 146-152) and **Garbage collection loop** (line 154-160) |\n| idle-cleanup/spec.md | `idle-cleanup/spec.md` | Idle timeout controller that deletes Sandboxes after 15min inactivity |\n| sandbox-orchestration/design.md | `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | Comprehensive design doc with all types, routes, GC, auth, store interface |\n| delta-spec.md | `delta-spec.md` (root) | WorkloadManager HTTP service spec including CRUD and delete endpoints |\n\n### Delete-related specifications (from specs, not yet implemented in code):\n\nFrom `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` (lines 146-152):\n- **DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId** and **DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId** routes are specified\n- Logic: load session from store, delete SandboxClaim or Sandbox based on stored Kind, treat NotFound as success, then DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n- Response: `200 {\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n\nFrom `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` (lines 154-160):\n- **Garbage collection loop**: ticks every 15s, queries inactive sessions (cutoff `now - 15m`, batch 16) and expired sessions (`before = now`, batch 16), deletes each workload then removes store entry\n\n### Key finding: **No delete handler implementation exists in code**\n\nThe grep for `handleDeleteSandbox`, `DeleteSandbox`, or `sandbox_delete` returned **zero results** in Go files. The delete endpoints are specified in the spec/design documents but have not been implemented yet.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Project Root Structure\n\n```\nagentcube/   (at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z)\n  .sdd_prompt.md\n  changes/              -- AR-001 through AR-006 (each with delta-spec.md, design.md, proposal.md, tasks.md)\n  ci-cd/\n  cli-toolkit/\n  client-go/            -- Generated Kubernetes typed client\n  code-execution/\n  coverage.out\n  delta-spec.md         -- Root-level delta spec (AR-004 WorkloadManager HTTP service)\n  deployment/\n  design.md\n  go.mod / go.sum\n  idle-cleanup/\n  integrations/\n  pkg/\n    apis/runtime/v1alpha1/   -- CRD type definitions (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, etc.)\n    workloadmanager/         -- HTTP server (handler/, middleware/, response/)\n  project.md\n  python-sdk/\n  sandbox-orchestration/     -- spec.md + design.md\n  session-routing/\n  session-store/\n  test_spec.md\n  testing/\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Key Findings\n\n1. **`pkg/workloadmanager`** has 5 Go files across 3 subdirectories. The `middleware/` directory is empty.\n2. **Multiple spec files** exist -- the most relevant being `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` (176 lines) and `delta-spec.md` (227 lines).\n3. **No `openspec` directory** exists in the project.\n4. **Sandbox delete functionality is specified but NOT implemented.** The spec defines `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` and `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` endpoints, a garbage collection loop, and idle cleanup controller -- but no corresponding Go handler files exist. Only `sandbox_create.go` is present with creation logic and a `rollbackCR` helper.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_288ff99b7ffeZizvkJWwC820I1","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775818008133,"end":1775818094628}}}}
